introduction = 'The idea is you paste a website of a company that you are interested in, it parses the website -> looks for the respective subdomains (e.g. products, locations etc.) then you select what parts of the website you are interested in, it scrapes them. then for each of the respective categories you have scraped it passes the content to an LLM (you can choose whether you want that to be Llama or ChatGPT (currently using 3.5 turbo) and then it creates a tabular output from the input for you that you can download as an excel'
